  <brief_title>Experience in Predicting Decision Making for Receiving Treatment in Acute Coronary Syndrome Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Cognitive Representation, Emotional Responses and Hospitalization Experience in Predicting Decision Making for Receiving Treatment Among Patients With Acute Coronary Syndrome</official_title>
